{"hash":"f32d25e1b609c4a1414f0349ab0f5c3f2e120801","data":{"post":{"id":"34dcf250c48aa86a3126a746dd1c9cfe","category":"기타","sub_category":"","title":"개발자 로드맵","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p>꾸준히 업데이트되고 있는 로드맵이다.</p>\n<p>해외 개발자들이 오픈소스로 정리하고 배포하는 프로젝트인데</p>\n<p>한글로 번역된 내용이 있어서 올려본다.</p>\n<p>무조건 정답이라고 할 순 없지만 충분히 도움이 되는 것 같다.</p>\n<p>(다른 파트 로드맵은... 사이트에서)</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"백엔드-개발자\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>백엔드 개발자</h2>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1286 3257' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-e923423570e8edf6bf834fc226989f91'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-e923423570e8edf6bf834fc226989f91)' width='1286' height='3257' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bE0YtHxUnLw/8QAGQEAAgMBAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAgMAAQQF/8QAMBEAAQQABAQFAgYDAAAAAAAAAQACAxEEEiExBRNBUSJhkaHBFDIjQnGBsfCC0eH/2gAMAwEAAhEDEQA/AP0PeRL9ulfaDu6gJk53Hnr8P0rpbws/MdvFIBwd0YPOfdvSvO0F4bK5iWK0jmMiM7AxknIKjr0HBNI37SYUZ022OegLUmTExxuyuOqYI3EWFQywy90%2b%2bygVNpyREoI4PP4qavKsNqZX3FUXcdqlj08gOTSXRrpL13S4sYotqBsbfUkfOi59UtW4DyBUk2v/AG2HQnPOOmRVOxULGCR7w1p6k1/KEscDVIuxu4rtXaEyYVsHfGyfuBSTt5fPpukrdQ6dcalIrgLb24Bc54yM%2blNF1iyZN6ykp13BGx%2b1b6hemCwlnh2sVUEZ6HJHuPX2ooMXBKS5jg8N3o360qLSNCvlh7X3jAD%2blNZUDkkx/TpVJ2O1%2bbWb6SG60K70zuCjRy3EaqJc5BCkcn1Nd5e1l2HIigiYDjxIc5HXo1G6R2gub%2b8tImRFEjEPhPIKx48WfIc4p31%2bFl8DI6J62UXJcNSmusaXaXzxS3TBGQFFJ248RHqOvAqf1HQba3MXcfaLhWDbirjIwOPynr8qcdrsjS0IOMTR8%2bHjn/dxUNcB3Zt8hcnBLKVwT8Rx%2blYMW5rTq2yR3TYwSLtWnZ6BVklKQSQ7kUHfgDqeOAMmuVz2ZaW5klS6Kh5GcjxeZzj8WMfCuHZgsJ5d0gdliAyrKQOfb%2bc0xntdXaaV4LtER2DAOeFGAMY2/wA1lxMMU%2bFbzY3PF7NNHrroW6ISSHmilqdmJBLJGbzPAI/F0OR/5U51ZNmlTKy78KBjH4uR/wDYNBWtrrTYma7iIcA4zg48vy0TqDXC6N